    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/pca_app_launch/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/pca_app_launch/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;High‑level description&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;highlevel-description&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#highlevel-description&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Program Compatibility Assistant (PCA) launch&lt;/strong&gt; plug‑in
provides a concise view of when and which binaries were invoked under PCA, which can be valuable for reconstructing system activity and identifying legacy or compatibility‑mode executions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Captures the exact path of every program launched via PCA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Records the precise launch time with sub‑second resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stores the data in a simple CSV‑compatible format for easy correlation with other forensic artefacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Helps identify usage of older or compatibility‑mode applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;File:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;configuration/pca_app_launch.xml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Plugin parser:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;Regexp&lt;/code&gt; (handled by the generic XML parser in &lt;code&gt;src/anssi_ogre_plugin/xml.py&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Timeline data&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;timeline-data&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#timeline-data&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The timeline displays the following elements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Timeline field&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Value&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Description&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;executable_path&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Full path of the executable launched by the PCA.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Fields&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;fields&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#fields&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Output Name&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Data Type&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Qualifier&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;timestamp&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;DateTime&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;executable_path&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;FILE_PATH&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/pca_general_record/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/pca_general_record/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;High‑level description&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;highlevel-description&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#highlevel-description&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Program Compatibility Assistant (PCA) General Record&lt;/strong&gt; plug‑in extracts each line of a PCA log. It captures when a program was launched, its status, executable location and associated metadata such as description, vendor, version, and exit code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reveals the exact time a program was started.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provides the executable’s full path for correlation with other artefacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Includes human‑readable file description, vendor and version for context.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Records the run status and exit code, useful for success/failure determination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;File:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;configuration/pca_general_record.xml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Plugin parser:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;Regexp&lt;/code&gt; (generic regular‑expression parser)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Timeline data&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;timeline-data&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#timeline-data&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The timeline displays the following elements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Timeline field&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Value&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;description&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;executable_path&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Full path of the launched executable.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;file_description&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Human‑readable description of the executable&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;### Fields&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Output Name&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Data Type&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Qualifier&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;run_time&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;DateTime&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;DATE_LAST_RUN&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;run_status&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Int&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;executable_path&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;FILE_PATH&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;file_description&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;software_vendor&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;PUBLISHER&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;file_version&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;program_id&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;APP_ID&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;exitcode_value&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;String&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;EXIT_CODE&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/wer/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/built-in-plugins/system-logs/wer/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h3&gt;High‑level description&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;highlevel-description&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#highlevel-description&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;WER&lt;/strong&gt; plug‑in parses Windows Error Reporting files, extracting metadata about crashes, hangs, and other failure events reported by the operating system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;File:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;configuration/wer.xml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Plugin parser:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;WER&lt;/code&gt; (implemented in &lt;code&gt;src/anssi_ogre_plugin/wer.py&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Timeline data&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;timeline-data&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#timeline-data&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;The timeline display the following elements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Timeline field&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Value&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Description&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;app_path&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;full path of the application that generated the report.&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Additional Description&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;event_type&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;type of the WER event (e.g., crash, hang).&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;original_file_name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
